         miti punarvacanam&nbsp;| <span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.2" target="_blank">kriyāḥ</a></span> itikartavyatā&nbsp;| <span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.2" target="_blank">lakṣaṇaṃ</a></span> sanniveśaparimāṇādi&nbsp;| atīteṣūpadeśo vyartha iti <span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.2" target="_blank">bhaviṣyadbhi</a></span>rityuktam&nbsp;| devānāṃ manasā sampatteḥ narairiti&nbsp;| nanu lakṣaṇaṃ
