      <p>nanu kiṃ <a href="" class="app" title="kriyādevocya <b&gt;म</b&gt;"><span class="appnum"><sup>1</sup></span></a>kriyai(yā ne)vocyata ityāha—<span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.5" target="_blank">divyānā</a></span>miti&nbsp;| śrūyatāmityanuvartate&nbsp;| narāṇāṃ kāryā kriyā itikartavyatā ca śrūyatām&nbsp;| cakārāllakṣaṇapūjane&nbsp;|
