         atra devādayo vivakṣitā na tu prayojyāḥ&nbsp;| teṣāṃ niyatasaṃkhyākatvāditi&nbsp;| tasyāsmadabhiprāyo
         na smṛtipathamāgataḥ sananapi daśarūpakādau | sa cānantarameva darśayiṣyate&nbsp;| (10-11)
