      <p><span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.12" target="_blank">pramāṇaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ</a></span> yannirdiṣṭamiti <a href="" class="app" title="jātā <b&gt;भन</b&gt;"><span class="appnum"><sup>1</sup></span></a>jātāvekavacanam&nbsp;|
