      <span class="pageinfo">[page 51]</span>
      
      <p>kāni pramāṇānītyāha—<span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.14" target="_blank">aṇu rajaścetyā</a></span>dinā&nbsp;| teṣāṃ lakṣaṇānyāha— <span class="mentioned"><a href=".html#N%C4%81%C5%9A%C4%81.2.14" target="_blank">aṇavo 'ṣṭā</a></span>vityādi&nbsp;| yataḥ prabhṛti dṛśyatā pravartate so 'ṇuḥ&nbsp;| aṇuḥ prasiddho 'ṇupariṇāmaḥ&nbsp;|
